{"tid":209451,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇跑步愛好者","createTime":"2017-04-20T08:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T04:14:33.000Z","uid":89608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cfc481b2592426532519b3f2e3a78ba03efb499","tid":209451,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"好鐘意跑步, 不斷跑將壓力發洩, 一直向前跑, 感覺跑步時精神只需要集中向前, <br />\n<br />\n個人都比較輕鬆啲, 只要一直跑, 個人就好似得到釋放;<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都鐘意跑步"},{"pid":"9476d31f6ee97dd404f4f91f06c1fc43ab390dd9","tid":209451,"uid":4955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"0aaae54098562ebb3b92795eb7e71132f28d3f2c","tid":209451,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:58:25.000Z","msg":"日日跑會唔會受傷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43dc72d7cb8c5edc426fb43fdca1f8c1c1f4d05","tid":209451,"uid":44808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:07:28.000Z","msg":"一個星期跑4次,一次7~9K,35~45分鐘<br />\n試過連續跑4日,第4日當晚對腳無哂力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4bcf636c93db410838745d4a13002f392d26af","tid":209451,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日跑會唔會受傷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一星期跑5 日, 冇問題"},{"pid":"e576996d062f4cd5ae8be12bf2c6bf7d4aea0e5f","tid":209451,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個星期跑4次,一次7~9K,35~45分鐘<br />\n試過連續跑4日,第4日當晚對腳無哂力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我通常運動一個鐘, 但唔會跑足, 跑到差不多會行, <br />\n<br />\n行到休息得差不多會再跑"},{"pid":"10430daa594dd7f0ff496a20f737acc52a23f0d7","tid":209451,"uid":50559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日跑會唔會受傷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因人而異，量力而為<br />\n初跑者不宜跑太密集"},{"pid":"5f70970a2e9fb65519245344aacb6fe6b4e06d4f","tid":209451,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176237812f02fb94643fb5c8f9fb0322b4991595","tid":209451,"uid":107147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日日跑會唔會受傷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因人而異，量力而為<br />\n初跑者不宜跑太密集</blockquote><br />\n密度可以慢慢上<br />\n跑得多你跑得密都唔會覺得攰<br />\n當然最重要係適合嘅裝束<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e7b61da8ec1a74e4c1c1f5ec5465c5553fad94","tid":209451,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T00:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a189a9b77734ae3304514b12eba3b9f86cc774e","tid":209451,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:01:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"634aabe7bb420c36a6a3b20b7be442293336465f","tid":209451,"uid":76926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:04:20.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔定期跑，通常一次跑2個鐘，跑4k <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b96770ac362d961ae0149d7070ec0e71f02dcb","tid":209451,"uid":48150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔定期跑，通常一次跑2個鐘，跑4k <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就咁行兩個鐘都應該唔止4k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ce6ed13d23ddcfaa81007028b24cf896c57a1a","tid":209451,"uid":15572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:14:27.000Z","msg":"我，一星期跑一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acdecf7d01cd0f1b2af35a7cc529c61e3594f1c","tid":209451,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:17:16.000Z","msg":"以前係去GYM房用跑步機跑, 但感覺差好遠, 用跑步機太舒服, 冇踩地既質感, <br />\n<br />\n係街跑地先至最正, 而且用力要大啲, 運動量高啲"},{"pid":"3b6a366a9bcb74b6f9770abbc79ec565003155f3","tid":209451,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前係去GYM房用跑步機跑, 但感覺差好遠, 用跑步機太舒服, 冇踩地既質感, <br />\n<br />\n係街跑地先至最正, 而且用力要大啲, 運動量高啲</blockquote><br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440f9c3265ac0921c66644f75bfd38a43901beb8","tid":209451,"uid":70042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:41:04.000Z","msg":"我習慣一個星期跑最少兩次<br />\n通常食飯前跑 而家個天氣跑到成身汁好正"},{"pid":"4d36dfa9a9f353adc91f2c15e2117aac3551d753","tid":209451,"uid":2379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:41:30.000Z","msg":"新手岩岩開始跑<br />\n每次跑得5-6K  30- 40分鐘度<br />\n一星期跑兩次<br />\n<br />\n大家有無咩訓練心得"},{"pid":"9b5f8056ce00615ee947b4db2b7b9a216354c50c","tid":209451,"uid":80805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"新手最近開始跑<br />\n隔日跑一次<br />\n6-8k 一粒半鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似好慢<br />\n夜跑好多野昅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2981e995452ed8c7e4362d2be6dd54a698082b82","tid":209451,"uid":27085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"1星期6日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a32522a43fea9b1bf50fc5e5a7f2add73e44ebd","tid":209451,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02