9451,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"跑步撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家工作問題冇跑好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  長跑真係要長時間跑先會搵到當中嘅樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42afa4634164657df0e26b9e8a33d812c430ffda","tid":209451,"uid":5827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我習慣一個星期跑最少兩次<br />\n通常食飯前跑 而家個天氣跑到成身<span style=\"color: red;\">汁</span>好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔爭氣咁笑左"},{"pid":"756bf3439320df732a967911d96ddb3481811e1b","tid":209451,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"呢排開始跑步，但係跑兩步就冇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d071171c1306c156fb217e4b8e340cdd55b69e27","tid":209451,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排開始跑步，但係跑兩步就冇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑慢D"},{"pid":"9a590b06c7f54d8c52dd52e66f5b58b9e154e7da","tid":209451,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排開始跑步，但係跑兩步就冇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慢慢黎, 好快會習慣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f407991877e2e3ba4682560b391d6be25f77ac50","tid":209451,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好撚鐘意跑荃灣西，來回嘉頓11k，夜晚跑個景真係無得頂！今晚唔落雨又去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪海邊條徑?</blockquote><br />\n係啊</blockquote><br />\n邊度開始<br />\n我唔夠氣, 通常去到近水灣就回頭"},{"pid":"9e978549abf7ed598ed5061d08dd3719bd7442bc","tid":209451,"uid":84918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:52:18.000Z","msg":"之前操左兩個月跑渣馬"},{"pid":"308f1df7829ee916ac5bc465f19eafd2a06af964","tid":209451,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3debcd2ced0176808c1650c51cc574ade3832dbd","tid":209451,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"10K一次超慢跑"},{"pid":"c888105fbdfdca6b64afaa9e89cf8154f405948d","tid":209451,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:31:21.000Z","msg":"跑開7k馬鞍山<br />\n唔知點解上唔到8k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228927532c2152f0d1326d08f0db81be12984b44","tid":209451,"uid":76926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:35:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔定期跑，通常一次跑2個鐘，跑4k <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就咁行兩個鐘都應該唔止4k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好慢咁跑，有時仲慢過行路，但無停過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23122e79b111c27e205452ae5f8da2444c89fe17","tid":209451,"uid":84918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑開7k馬鞍山<br />\n唔知點解上唔到8k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑慢d"},{"pid":"eca1b5cab658f9873922f0b029396008aee1593a","tid":209451,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好撚鐘意跑荃灣西，來回嘉頓11k，夜晚跑個景真係無得頂！今晚唔落雨又去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪海邊條徑?</blockquote><br />\n係啊</blockquote><br />\n邊度開始<br />\n我唔夠氣, 通常去到近水灣就回頭</blockquote><br />\n荃灣西站近碼頭有個起點嘅牌架，就係果度開始跑。到嘉頓就返轉頭，終點都係荃灣西。"},{"pid":"22438ace878aa40c55128722bb391863d9216843","tid":209451,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好撚鐘意跑荃灣西，來回嘉頓11k，夜晚跑個景真係無得頂！今晚唔落雨又去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪海邊條徑?</blockquote><br />\n係啊</blockquote><br />\n邊度開始<br />\n我唔夠氣, 通常去到近水灣就回頭</blockquote><br />\n荃灣西站近碼頭有個起點嘅牌架，就係果度開始跑。到嘉頓就返轉頭，終點都係荃灣西。</blockquote><br />\n巴打跑左幾多年<br />\n<br />\n我跑左一年左右<br />\n一星期4,5 日 都係個個距離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣可以跑咁遠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我跑完來回都已經無氣+少少暈"},{"pid":"402fc66393a7a74df41dce08880487001571b6e8","tid":209451,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好撚鐘意跑荃灣西，來回嘉頓11k，夜晚跑個景真係無得頂！今晚唔落雨又去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪海邊條徑?</blockquote><br />\n係啊</blockquote><br />\n邊度開始<br />\n我唔夠氣, 通常去到近水灣就回頭</blockquote><br />\n荃灣西站近碼頭有個起點嘅牌架，就係果度開始跑。到嘉頓就返轉頭，終點都係荃灣西。</blockquote><br />\n巴打跑左幾多年<br />\n<br />\n我跑左一年左右<br />\n一星期4,5 日 都係個個距離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣可以跑咁遠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我跑完來回都已經無氣+少少暈</blockquote><br />\n我跑就跑左好多年架啦，中學開始到依家十年度，中間爆過肺抖左两三年，近呢两年跑返，不過跑唔返之前個成績。<br />\n我之前就跟跑會，依家就自己跑，你自己慢慢加長啲距離就得架啦。"},{"pid":"e2d0cf982b8979e603f0db5a205c56bc05a7b189","tid":209451,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd38c9e87cb866aac3c845d6e54a91d3e3d0d677","tid":209451,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑開7k馬鞍山<br />\n唔知點解上唔到8k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊跑包上到"},{"pid":"b70f66bd074d359ee1597ccab68b8135c7fd305f","tid":209451,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:53:10.000Z","msg":"一星期跑1-2次<br />\n加埋 15-20 km <br />\n跑得唔快<br />\n10km 大概要55分鐘左右<br />\n<br />\n啱啱個星期一由屯門跑出荃灣<br />\n半馬距離<br />\n好攞命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06256fc6e75a5e1ec78e95cac4b247641e7156aa","tid":209451,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"胡師傅屌鳩你班傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fef267c52ac6433337e6aad4ae824e01d2656b3","tid":209451,"uid":92921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"試過跑左轉台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307ea81cc9d4f5a8ff990b249ebc54a4f239179a","tid":209451,"uid":13035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"之前隔日跑 每之一個鐘<br />\n跑左一排足弓位痛<br />\n點可以好返<br />\n好想去跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c2a4206a719bf2b450cff2510a2b31a3a2823e","tid":209451,"uid":92921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前隔日跑 每之一個鐘<br />\n跑左一排足弓位痛<br />\n點可以好返<br />\n好想去跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n按摩足底筋膜"},{"pid":"10cf876391e8f804d1662a6bd55be99320871b27","tid":209451,"uid":13035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前隔日跑 每之一個鐘<br />\n跑左一排足弓位痛<br />\n點可以好返<br />\n好想去跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n按摩足底筋膜</blockquote><br />\n有時有按 半個月都仲痛痛地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}